Carrot Bunny Thinlits Die Set by Tim Holtz - 11 pieces

This adorable bunny is perfect for those whimsical creations. The die cuts the edging of the bunny front paws such that it can appear to be holding items or peeking out of a rabbit hole. Set also includes a carrot dies. This 11 piece die set by Tim Holtz has intricate detail and offers many creative opportunities. Dies include: 1 Bunny Rabbit, 2 carrot bases, 2 carrot layers, 4 carrot tops and layers, bunny ears, cheeks and face.
Approximate sizing: bunny 3 x 1.25 inches, large carrot 4.25 inches, small carrot 2 inches
Woven 3-D Textured Impressions Embossing Folder by Lynda Kanase - A6 Size 4.25 x 6.128 inches
Thinlits and 3-d textured impressions embossing folders are compatible with the BIGkick, Big Shot and Vagabond machines. Machines are sold separately and not included with this set.
description: Thinlits create dazzling detailed shapes for more creative cardmaking and papercrafting projects. These wafer-thin chemically-etched die sets are designed to cut, emboss or stencil a single sheet of cardstock, paper, metallic foil or vellum. They are simple to use, compact and portable for cutting at home or on the go. Use them for enhanced intricacy and to add a special touch of inspiration to all your projects. The Thinlits dies in this set are compatible with the BIGkick, Big Shot and Vagabond machines.
